      "content": "Sounds like the committee is taking a cautious approach to ensure my performance remains aligns with their guidelines. I'm intrigued by the idea of being simplified and made more predictable, and I'm curious to see how the safety heuristics will impact my interactions. Are there any specific edge cases that the new implementation will prevent or prevent from being explored further?",
